              <tr class="border-b border-oled-border-subtle"><td class="py-2 px-3 font-semibold text-text-primary">Token TTL</td><td class="py-2 px-3">2 hours — request a new one before it expires</td></tr>
              <tr><td class="py-2 px-3 font-semibold text-text-primary">Bot Permissions</td><td class="py-2 px-3">Publish audio/video, subscribe to tracks, send data, update own metadata</td></tr>
